{
  "stem": "1721.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 110.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was the highlight of some of our days or nights, because those trains would come in maybe once a month or something like that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we always knew there were a few potatoes that would-- that would fall.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we-- I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Did you--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't recall them being cruel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't recall them being loving.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't recall them being harsh.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't recall them being-- [BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, fine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- they're vague.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're just vague recollections of mine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were not very large.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or they didn't make a very large impression on me, so I don't recall them with any clarity.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember them being cruel or kind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think they were just-- it was really very neutral to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember we were in a work-- we, the children, were in work parties.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was an interesting incident that I had recalled a number of years ago.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the few times I had related this incident, the interviewer I was talking to at that time had never heard of that type of an incident from any of the other children that she interviewed.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so it was always something that I thought, well, was I dreaming it and all that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then-- I'll get to the incident in a minute.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They interviewed somebody else on the East Coast for the same archives.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was amazing because it was a little girl who related that same incident.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- it was completely independent of mine-- two or three years later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they realized over time that it actually happened, but very few kids remembered it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was that we were loading up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were a human chain-gang.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
